    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "In addition, we need to be vigilant towards the information manipulation by foreign actors to steer further violence and instability. Those foreign actors do not share our vision for a stable and inclusive Syria.\nIt is for the EU to support the transition and to become a reliable partner for Syria's future. The coming days and months will be decisive."
      }
    ],
