  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_315",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_315"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_230"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_233"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Integrate our 27 little armies to fight as one. As President Zelenskyy said, the time has come for the armed forces of Europe to be created. So let's take the first concrete steps today. Make NATO's command and control European so we can operate as one. Jointly procure strategic enablers so we can fight effectively. Create permanent multinational units so we can get 50 extra brigades.\nEurope is a peace project, but how can we be strong enough to defend it? The answer to that existential question is simple and consists of three things: Unite! Unite! Unite!\nLet's not wait for war to unite us. Let's unite to prevent war. And to my Dutch colleagues in the national parliament who just voted against the REARM plans from Ms von der Leyen, I say you're making a massive mistake."
      },
      {
        "@value": "En effet, cette proposition impliquerait d’obliger des États à reconnaître des filiations issues de mères porteuses, alors que leur loi nationale l’interdit. Les États membres seraient donc contraints de valider indirectement des pratiques contraires à leur législation nationale et à leurs choix politiques et éthiques. Ce forcing consisterait à faire reconnaître de fait la GPA et à faciliter sa pratique, pourtant interdite dans plusieurs États européens, comme la France. La légalisation de la marchandisation du corps de la femme est, en fin de compte, la véritable intention de ce règlement scandaleux. Tous ceux qui prétendent défendre les droits des femmes et des enfants devraient se mobiliser contre cela."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T17:52:23"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T18:19:13"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_262",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
