      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PPE"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#name": [
      {
        "@value": "Merja KyllÃ¶nen"
      },
      {
        "@value": "Łukasz Kohut"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_330",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_330"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_25"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_242"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "If we are weak, we are a target. If we are strong, we are safe. This is the principle that needs to guide us. This is why I say invest more in defence, to keep our citizens safe and invest more in common European projects in defence.\nCommissioner Kubilius, we very much welcome the work that you're doing, and we're very much looking forward to the white paper that you're going to propose. Our expectation is to see projects in there which we at European level can do better that than Member States can do alone. And then we should also find the funds, the resources, to support the projects which the European Commission puts forward. We should show to the people of Europe that spending money at European level on defence is worth it, and that it is better spent than at national level."
      },
      {
        "@value": "Mums ir jāturpina militāri atbalstīt Ukrainu visiem iespējamiem līdzekļiem. Tāpēc neatliekami ir jāpieņem lēmums par Krievijas iesaldēto aktīvu izmantošanu Ukrainas apbruņošanai un atjaunošanai. Puspasākumu un kompromisu laiks ir beidzies. Eiropai ir jārīkojas ātri, vienoti un izlēmīgi. Liksim Putinam maksāt par agresijas noziegumu un izlietajām ukraiņu tautas asinīm."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T18:17:06"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T18:42:10"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_343",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_343"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_247"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_251"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Notre stratÃ©gie doit reposer sur notre Ã©mancipation de la dÃ©fense amÃ©ricaine et sâappuyer sur une force europÃ©enne permanente, dotÃ©e de son propre commandement et capable de dÃ©fendre nos intÃ©rÃªts et nos valeurs. Elle doit Ãªtre fondÃ©e sur le respect du droit international, un droit que nous devons dÃ©fendre, de Gaza Ã  lâUkraine. Notre place est aux cÃ´tÃ©s des peuples qui se battent pour la justice. Nous aurions dÃ» Ãªtre aux cÃ´tÃ©s de lâAfrique du Sud devant la Cour internationale de justice. Nous aurions dÃ» soutenir la Ligue arabe dans son plan de reconstruction de Gaza face au diktat de Trump.\nLâUnion europÃ©enne ne peut plus rester spectatrice. Elle ne peut plus garder le silence sur les grandes initiatives de notre monde. Elle nâa plus le droit dâavoir peur. Elle doit sâÃ©manciper et agir."
      },
      {
        "@value": "I höstas beslutade vi att skicka avkastningen av de frysta ryska tillgångarna till Ukraina. Nu är det dags att ta nästa steg och frigöra själva tillgångarna som bara i Europa uppgår till runt 200 miljarder euro. Europas finansiella institutioner och marknader ska inte vara ett redskap för krigsherrar att säkra sina tillgångar i skydd av våra rättssystem. Ryssland ska betala! Slava Ukraini!"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
