        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T21:35:45"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_546",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_546"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_379"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "The recent obstruction of a European Parliament delegation and the deportation of MEPs and EU officials is an affront to our democratic processes, and I want to express my solidarity to my constituency colleague and Chair of the delegation, Lynn Boylan. You mess with one Dub; you mess with all Dubs! We stand with you, Lynn, in demanding the strongest possible response from President Metsola.\nFar from business as usual, Israel must face sanctions now! Saoirse don PhalaistÃ­n!"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T23:09:12"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_300",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_300"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_80"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_224"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Herr Kommissar, Sie werden Menschenrechte mit FÃ¼Ãen treten mit Ihren VorschlÃ¤gen. Sie haben noch nicht mal eine Liste von Drittstaaten, die Sie uns vorschlagen wollen, aber Sie scheinen sehr zuversichtlich zu sein, dass Sie genug Autokraten in dieser Welt finden, die sich mit Ihnen auf diesen dreckigen Deal einlassen. Ich finde es wirklich bemerkenswert, Herr Kommissar, wie viele RechtsauÃenparteien heute Ihnen die Hand geschÃ¼ttelt haben bei dieser Debatte.\nHerr Kommissar, wenn Sie wirklich LÃ¶sungen suchen wollen, auch fÃ¼r das Thema der Migration, dann tun Sie was dafÃ¼r, dass Menschen nicht mehr ihre Heimat verlassen mÃ¼ssen. Tun Sie was dafÃ¼r, dass die EUâStaaten nicht mehr Waffen in alle Welt schicken. Tun Sie was gegen den Klimawandel, der zu einer neuen Fluchtursache wird. Tun Sie was dagegen, wie die multinationalen europÃ¤ischen Konzerne den globalen SÃ¼den ausplÃ¼ndern. Tun Sie was ...\n(Die PrÃ¤sidentin entzieht der Rednerin das Wort.)"
      },
      {
        "@value": "Let's clarify this: we have the freedom of movement for goods, services, capital and people in the EU. Article 21 of the EU Treaty states, 'Every citizen of the Union shall have the right to move and reside freely within the territory of all the Member States'. Similarly, Article 45 of the EU Charter of Fundamental Rights affirms, 'Every citizen of the Union has the right to move and reside freely within the territory of the Member States'. So what is the far right doing here today? The only correct answer is that you are doing an exercise in homophobia and an attempt to deprive children of their parents.\nCommissioner, the worst part, I must say, is that, at a time when we need to strengthen protection against far-right hate, the Commission has chosen to withdraw the proposal for the EU anti-discrimination directive – I must say that that is very disappointing. But now let us ensure we can adopt a piece of legislation that would let families be families, regardless of where they move in our Union."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T17:22:59"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T18:02:31"
      }
    ]
  },
