    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Cette annÃ©e, les travailleurs de lâacier et de lâautomobile annoncent 300Â 000Â licenciements. Une entreprise ne devrait pas pouvoir distribuer des dividendes record une annÃ©e et licencier lâannÃ©e suivante. En France, on appelle cela la privatisation des profits et la collectivisation des pertes, ce qui crÃ©e un immense sentiment dâinjustice et entraÃ®ne la montÃ©e des populismes. Il faudrait dÃ©sormais conditionner le soutien Ã  lâÃ©conomie et aux entreprises Ã  la participation des salariÃ©s et des pouvoirs publics Ã  leur gouvernance. Câest lÃ  la vraie nouvelle donne."
      },
      {
        "@value": "We must demand the release of the 23 Armenian prisoners of war who are being subjected to sham trials, violations of due process and trumped‑up charges. In this regard, it's particularly important for the International Criminal Court to investigate the cases submitted by the Ombudsman of Nagorno-Karabakh and provide a judicial response to the cases of forced expulsion and ethnic cleansing committed by Azerbaijan against the Armenian population of Artsakh.\nAs this violent approach by Azerbaijan has the whole Armenian community in its sights, I have a direct question to High Commissioner Kallas: are you ready to impose the same sanctions against Aliyev if he invades Armenia, as the European Union has imposed against Putin after the invasion of Ukraine?"
      }
    ],
