    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "The US has also been a long-term partner, but now it seems that President Trump is using the divide-and-rule model known since Roman times to get China off Russia's side to divide Europe and oppress others under its own power.\nOne should not side with those who dream of Tsarist power or world empire. MrÂ Toveri, how do we find European cooperation and understand that the situation is that only a united and strong Europe, which covers its powers in all areas of activity, will survive?"
      },
      {
        "@value": "Written Statements (Rule 178)"
      }
    ],
