    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#name": [
      {
        "@value": "Presidente."
      },
      {
        "@value": "Petra Steger"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_394",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_394"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_282"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "For too long, Ireland has overlooked security and defence. While we remain committed to military neutrality, it does not equate to vulnerability. Securing our territorial waters and airspace is crucial, and the Government is prioritising the much-needed investment in our defence forces.\nThat is why I support Ireland's increased ambition in terms of urgent investment in primary radar, naval expansion and air defence. These are not luxuries: they are fundamental to our national security.\nAt the same time, Ireland's commitment to neutrality remains steadfast. But neutrality must be fit for purpose for the 21st century. That means contributing meaningfully to European security and contributing in areas in which we have a considerable degree of experience and expertise â like peacekeeping, for example.\nIt's time to get off the fence and get on with defence."
      },
      {
        "@value": "Kvôli vašej greendealovej zelenej politike a sankčnej politike máme v Európe najdrahšie ceny energií na celom, celučičkom svete. Plyn máme päťkrát drahší ako v Spojených štátoch amerických a vy teraz hovoríte, že treba ešte viac sankcií a ešte viac ten plyn zdražiť. Toto je váš plán? Toto je vaša ponuka pre európsky priemysel, pre európskych obyvateľov? Ešte viac zdražovania, ešte viac problémov, ešte viac likvidácie európskych firiem?\nV žiadnom prípade s týmto nesúhlasíme a žiadame presný opak: zrušiť nezmyselné energetické sankcie. Nech si majú firmy možnosť vybrať najlacnejšieho dodávateľa, pre mňa za mňa z celého sveta, ale nech majú obyvatelia a európsky priemysel cenovo dostupné, lacné energie.\n(Rečník súhlasil, že odpovie na otázku položenú zdvihnutím modrej karty)"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
