    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "VyzÃ½vÃ¡m proto Komisi, aby prioritnÄ ÅeÅ¡ila problÃ©m zvanÃ½ ETS. ETS1 musÃ­ bÃ½t pÅedvÃ­datelnÄjÅ¡Ã­ a ETS2 musÃ­ bÃ½t minimÃ¡lnÄ o dva roky odloÅ¾ena. Co ale potÅebujeme nejvÃ­ce, je levnÃ¡ energie pro naÅ¡e firmy. UvidÃ­me, jak budou vypadat konkrÃ©tnÃ­ legislativnÃ­ nÃ¡vrhy, ale zatÃ­m dohodu o ÄistÃ©m prÅ¯myslu hodnotÃ­m jako hodnÄ promarnÄnou pÅÃ­leÅ¾itost."
      },
      {
        "@value": "That's why I think it is very important that we start doing a cost-benefit analysis on what these companies actually bring to the European Union and what harm they bring. If the decision is that they are more harmful than actually beneficial, then maybe they don't belong in the European Union."
      }
    ],
