  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_165",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_165"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_121"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_118"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_129"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "We have faced various crises â one after the other â and every time we have proven that we are stronger when tested. We have delivered vaccines to our citizens in record time; we secured gas supplies when Russia cut them off; we tackled economic turmoil. And every time there was talk about disunity, we proved we can succeed.\nToday we face yet another situation, where our closest ally often sounds like an adversary, and that makes us feel threatened and uncertain. And at the beginning of this plenary, I want us to remember the words of Robert Schuman, who said: 'Europe will not be made at once [...]. It will be built through concrete achievements which first create a de facto solidarity'. It is the moment of solidarity where words turn into actions, because words do not build Europe."
      },
      {
        "@value": "Alors, oui Ã  un fÃ©minisme qui dÃ©fend vraiment les femmes, comme le collectif NÃ©mÃ©sis, qui dÃ©nonce ces hypocrisies. Oui Ã  un soutien rÃ©el Ã  leur carriÃ¨re et Ã  leur vie familiale, sans idÃ©ologie ni culpabilisation. LâÃ©galitÃ© ne se construira pas dans la compromission avec ceux qui prÃ´nent la soumission des femmes.\n(L'oratrice accepte une question carton bleu)"
      },
      {
        "@value": "Zatímco USA a Čína budují sílu a prosperitu svých firem, Evropa páchá ekonomickou a geopolitickou sebevraždu. Tato Komise nemá jako prioritu bezpečnost, boj proti nelegální migraci ani náš průmysl. Jediná priorita je udržet si přízeň a zelenou politiku. Komise selhává v diplomacii i v ochraně evropského života. Je potřeba vrátit se k realitě, pomoci našim firmám, zamezit nelegální migraci a především být tu pro naše občany."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-10T21:19:18"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T14:04:31"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T14:38:42"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_378",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"
