    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "So Europe has to grow up and be strong â both economically and militarily â so that we can take care of our own independently, hopefully with good cooperation with the United States some time after Trump's term. But if not, we still have to be able to do it independently. We have people, we have money, we have innovation. We can do it."
      },
