    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Europe must reclaim its own security. We are at the beginning of an important journey to develop a European army. Together we can turn our vision into reality, but this will require strong commitment from all of us.\nThis is not just about buying equipment. It's about coming together. We must address challenges with a united military force. We need to significantly expand our military capabilities. Yes, challenges will come, just as they did with introducing a common currency â the euro. But today, the euro is a pillar of European stability. Tomorrow we have to add a European army."
      },
      {
        "@value": "Ez óriási versenyképességi hátrányt okoz, ezért zárnak be gyárak Európa-szerte. Ezért van arról szó Németországban is, hogy bezárják-e például a Volkswagen-gyárat. Hogyha megemelkednek az energiaárak, abból Európa nem jön ki jól, a gazdasági versenyképesség hanyatlani fog."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
