    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Poate nu ar mai trebui nici noi sÄ dorim rÄzboi, poate nu ar trebui sÄ cheltuim 800 de miliarde pe Ã®narmare Èi poate ar trebui sÄ cÄutÄm soluÈii. Ce soluÈii sunt? DacÄ PreÈedinta Parlamentului European, doamna Roberta Metsola, a fost la Washington, am Ã®nÈeles cÄ a mers la cimitirul Arlington, dar n-a ajuns sÄ se Ã®ntÃ¢lneascÄ cu Vance sau cu Trump. Atunci de ce s-a dus acolo, sÄ viziteze un cimitir? Poate dÃ¢nsele ar trebui sÄ-Èi dea demisia, sÄ punem alÈi lideri importanÈi Ã®n funcÈiile care conteazÄ Èi sÄ stÄm la masÄ cu Trump pentru a gÄsi soluÈii de pace, cÄci altfel o sÄ ne ducem Ã®n... (cÃ¢teva cuvinte care nu se aud)"
      },
      {
        "@value": "Some in this Parliament do not like the idea of reducing fossil fuel use; it reminds them too much of Greta Thunberg, and she scares them. And since we are all woke, we must respect their feelings. But we cannot change geology, and that means that any European economy dependent on gas or oil will eventually find itself in the shoes of President Zelenskyy – facing blackmail and extortion, whether it be in the Oval Office or at the end of a very long table in the Kremlin.\nSo, colleagues, let us at least spare our economies, our businesses and our citizens that fate by making the transition work."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
