  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_361",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_361"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_261"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_214"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Those who say that Russia is not a threat normally come from countries that has not been attacked, occupied, raped and pillaged dozens of times through history like Finland, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Poland and many other countries have. Don't lecture us about peaceful Russia, we know better!\nEurope has finally â after decades of inaction â started to take the right steps towards our security and defence. Let us continue on this path.\nI have three children, all in the Finnish army reserves, ready to defend us all. I want them to be properly equipped to do that. We must and we can afford to do that. Otherwise, saying that is not true, it is a lie.\nAnd to those who claim that Russia's defence budget is much smaller than Europe's, please Google purchasing power parity and the Russian defence budget â you will be surprised.\n(The speaker agreed to take a blue-card question)"
      },
      {
        "@value": "For this reason, the assets of the Central Bank of Russia shall remain immobilised until Russia pays for the damage it has caused in Ukraine. The Commission fully supports exploring all possible avenues to aid Ukraine in obtaining compensation from Russia, consistent with our respective legal systems and international law.\nWe need to continue to signal to Russia that our support to Ukraine will be sustained, broad-based and steadfast. Looking ahead, our priority is to work closely with international partners to ensure the successful completion of the IMF programme to guarantee that Ukraine has sufficient resources to counter Russia's aggression. This includes ensuring the full implementation of the G7 ERA loan initiative by all G7 partners in the coming months.\nTo conclude, let me also add that we need to be mindful of the challenges that lie ahead of us, especially in a context where the EU will need to step up its efforts to support Ukraine's defence and financial needs.\nThank you for letting have the opportunity to participate in this very important debate."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T18:57:10"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T19:19:46"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_334",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_334"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_78"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_244"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Ten tweede, commissaris, maakt u gebruik van artikelÂ 122 van het Verdrag om het Parlement buitenspel te zetten. Van mij mag het, maar dat gaat de kwaliteit niet verbeteren. Een goed Europees defensiebeleid voer je niet in achterkamertjes.\nTen derde, commissaris, komt u volgende week met een witboek. Ik hoop dat het duidelijker en concreter is dan u vandaag bent geweest. Er moeten echt grote Europese programmaâs in staan en een routekaart voor een Europees leger. Ook dit zeg ik hier al tien jaar. U wilt de geschiedenis ingaan? Wel, commissaris, maak die routekaart voor dat Europees leger, of u mist de afspraak met de geschiedenis."
      },
      {
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
