  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_491",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_491"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_14"
      },
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_335"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "I really beg everyone who is speaking today to keep the time, because we are already very late.\nAnd I announce directly at the beginning that we can just take five people for the catch-the-eye procedure. So we will open it shortly and then I will close it when we have five announced, because otherwise we will be here until midnight."
      },
      {
        "@value": "Mr President, Commissioner, esteemed colleagues, let us not fail the people of Bosnia again. We failed them as we watched the first genocide after the Holocaust unroll in front of our eyes in July 1995, in Srebrenica. We failed them when we watched concentration camps built where Bosnians were systematically murdered, tortured, raped, starved. We failed them when we watched Sarajevo be under siege for three long years.\nThe time for press releases is over. It's time to act! Impose swift sanctions on those who are breaching the Dayton peace agreement. Strengthen our EUFOR mission so we can keep the peace. And continue the support to the Bosnian legal system and institutions, with the aim for them to become members of the EU. Do not let the people of Bosnia down again. Never forget Srebrenica!"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-11T21:38:17"
      },
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-12T22:21:40"
      }
    ]
