      {
        "@value": "Continuing the unwavering EU support for Ukraine, after three years of Russia’s war of aggression (RC-B10-0156/2025, B10-0156/2025, B10-0158/2025, B10-0159/2025, B10-0161/2025, B10-0163/2025, B10-0165/2025, B10-0166/2025, B10-0168/2025) (vote)"
